programme.title: Jurassic World: Fallen Kingdom
programme.desc: Four years after the Jurassic World theme park was closed down and the eruption of a dormant volcano on the island, Owen (Chris Pratt) and Claire (Bryce Dallas Howard) return to Isla Nubar to save the dinosaurs before they extinguish.(n)

programme.title: Nick of Time
programme.desc: Gene Watson is an average accountant whose life takes a disturbing turn when his daughter is kidnapped at a train station, and he's blackmailed to kill a politician in 90 minutes or she will be killed.(n)

programme.title: Eagle Eye
programme.desc: Jerry and Rachel meet each other through a mysterious phone call from a woman they've never met, threatening their lives and pushing them into a chain of risky situations by using modern technology and carefully monitoring their movements.(n)

programme.title: Double Take
programme.desc: When he gets entangled in a dangerous conspiracy, the banker Daryl goes on the run to avoid being killed. programme.title: Toy Soldiers
programme.desc: When their boarding school is overtaken by terrorists, a group of rebellious and troublemaking boys decide to stand up to them.(n)

programme.title: Bumblebee
programme.desc: On the run in the year of 1987, Bumblebee finds refuge in a junkyard in a small Californian beach town and is found by Charlie, an 18 year old girl who is trying to find her place in the world. When Charlie revives him, she discovers that this is no ordinary, yellow VW bug.(n)

programme.desc: An unknown IT company builds a time-machine, and tests it by moving Professor Edward to 14-century France. A team is then formed including two students and an archaeologist, to travel through time to retrieve him. Will they be able to succeed on a mission that's the first of its kind.(n)

programme.title: RoboCop
programme.desc: Set in a dystopian future where crime rates have become insanely high, evil corporation Omni Consumer Products tries to create a prototype that is half-robot and half-human. When RoboCop learns about their intrigues, he turns on his masters.(n)

programme.title: The Divergent Series: Allegiant
programme.desc: Tris and Four make the hard decision to leave their home behind in an attempt to find a way to save Chicago from turmoil. However, they end up being taken to a city of hidden secrets where they end up learning the backstory of how their world became what it is.(n)
